# Prediction Lab Rules

- Every AB test / model experiment MUST be displayed on the Prediction Lab dashboard page, not just printed in terminal.
- Each experiment card should show: model name, key metrics (AUC, Precision, Recall, F1), event backtest results, and current prediction.
- When adding a new experiment, keep previous experiments visible for side-by-side comparison.
